Visualize most frequent word for each topic

Step 3: Clustering Analysis for presidents

Clutering using Kmeans prediction

we see that Franklin D Roosvelt, William Cliton are in the same cluster, george washington_bush and Donald Trump are in the same cluster etc. The results indicates a potential relationship between speech topic and party.
